[27/01/2019 21:32:30] <font color="#ffffff">(Aplausos)</font>
[27/01/2019 21:32:41] <font color="#ffffff">Bien, gracias, Robert "For".</font>
[27/01/2019 21:32:45] <font color="#ffffff">Tengo un regalo.</font>
