[27/01/2019 21:33:40] <font color="#ffffff">en nuestra casa de hombres.</font>
[27/01/2019 21:33:41] <font color="#ffffff">(Aplausos)</font>
[27/01/2019 21:33:47] <font color="#ffffff">Mis amigos,</font>
[27/01/2019 21:33:47] <font color="#ffffff">Robert "For", ustedes, yo,</font>
